comments.comment:
An internationally-known serial killer.
They were called, Jack the Ripper.
Jack brutally murdered five women and despite the best efforts of Scotland Yard, Jack vanished without ever being caught.

Height/Weight: 134cm, 33kg
Origin: History
Region: London
Alignment: Chaotic-Evil
Gender: Female
The version of Jack summoned as an Assassin.

Since Jack the Ripper's identity was never found out, their form changes in accordance with the class they are summoned into.
As an Assassin, they represent the collective consciousness of those who were never given the chance to be born.

Since Assassin Jack was killed before she was born, her wish to the Grail is to return to her mother's womb.
She is naive, but perhaps because she was summoned as Jack the Ripper, she is astonishingly intuitive.

『Maria the Ripper』
Rank: D~B
NP Type: Anti-Personnel
This Noble Phantasm recreates the murders of Jack the Ripper.
There are three conditions must be met: it must be night, there must be fog, and the target must be a woman.

After being summoned as an Assassin, she calls herself "Jack the Ripper," but even she doesn't know if she's the real killer.
She remembers killing several women, but is uncertain if they are Jack's victims.

As a child who was never loved, she strongly seeks love.
She desires a mother's love from her Master, be they male or female.
You're free to respond to her wishes, but don't be surprised if she crawls into your belly.

voiceLines.name: Birthday
voiceLines.subtitle: The day you were born? Is that really worth celebrating?

voiceLines.name: During an Event
voiceLines.subtitle: Something is wrong. Let's check it out.

voiceLines.name: Conversation 1
voiceLines.subtitle: C'mon, Mommy. Let's go, let's go!

voiceLines.name: Conversation 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Mhm. Mommy will always be Mommy.

voiceLines.name: Likes
voiceLines.subtitle: Good memories? Sleeping on a warm bed feels good, doesn't it?

voiceLines.name: About the Holy Grail
voiceLines.subtitle: A wish for the Holy Grail... All we want is to go back inside Mommy. That's all we want.

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 2
voiceLines.subtitle: You want to do something that hurts? We don't like pain... Why do you do hurtful things? ...You don't?

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 3
voiceLines.subtitle: Hmm... As long as it doesn't hurt, it's okay.

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 5
voiceLines.subtitle: Can you hug us tight? Please? We'd do anything for you, Mommy.

voiceLines.name: Ascension 3
voiceLines.subtitle: [id 600500_0_G040]What do you think? Are we cute?

voiceLines.name: Ascension 4
voiceLines.subtitle: [id 600500_0_G050]Hm, why do you love us so much?

voiceLines.name: Summon
text: Assassin Jack the Ripper[r]Nice to meet you, Mother.
voiceLines.subtitle:
Assassin Jack the Ripper
Nice to meet you, Mother.

voiceLines.name: Victory 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Let us cut you up, okay?

voiceLines.name: Victory 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Oh, look at you, all chopped up.

voiceLines.name: Noble Phantasm
voiceLines.subtitle:
[id 600500_0_B050]Hell starts here. We are the fire, the rain, the power... Let the slaughter begin. 
[id 600500_0_B056]Maria the Ripper!
